<main class="main top-main">
  <div class="top-message">
    <h2>How to Use</h2>
  </div>

  <%# Section: Genotype Input Instructions %>
  <div class="how-to-use-section">
    <h1>Genotype Input Steps</h1>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <p>1. Pick "Genotype from DNA Test" in the main menu.</p>
        <%= image_tag "pick_gene.svg", alt: "Step 1 - Pick Genotype from DNA Test" %>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>2. Fill the gene code and zygosity for each gene (from both parents).</p>
        <%= image_tag "fill_gen_phen.svg", alt: "Step 2 - Fill Gene Code and Zygosity" %>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>3. Make sure at least the gene code of the phenotype (disease) to be searched is included.</p>
        <%= image_tag "zygosity.svg", alt: "Step 3 - Confirm Required Gene Code" %>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>4. Enter the phenotype (disease name). It must match exactly as listed in <code>ontology.jax.org</code>.</p>
        <%= image_tag "add_row.svg", alt: "Step 4 - Enter Phenotype" %>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>5. Add or delete gene rows as needed using the '+' and 'âœ•' buttons.</p>
        <%= image_tag "delete_row.svg", alt: "Step 5 - Add/Delete Rows" %>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>6. Click "Process Genetic Data" to start the analysis.</p>
        <%= image_tag "start.svg", alt: "Step 6 - Process Genetic Data" %>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>7. The results will be displayed below after the Ontology API finishes processing.</p>
        <%= image_tag "result.svg", alt: "Step 7 - View Result" %>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <%# Section: Phenotype Input Instructions %>
  <div class="how-to-use-section">
    <h1>Phenotype Input Steps</h1>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <p>1. Pick "Phenotypes" in the main menu.</p>
        <%= image_tag "pick_gene.svg", alt: "Step 1 - Pick Phenotypes Option" %>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>2. Enter the phenotype (disease name) and whether the mother and father have the disease.</p>
        <%= image_tag "fill_gen_phen.svg", alt: "Step 2 - Input Parental Phenotypes" %>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>3. Ensure disease names match those in <code>ontology.jax.org</code> exactly.</p>
        <%= image_tag "zygosity.svg", alt: "Step 3 - Match Disease Name" %>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>4. Add more diseases using the "+ Add" button if calculating multiple phenotypes.</p>
        <%= image_tag "add_row.svg", alt: "Step 4 - Add More Phenotypes" %>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>5. Click "Process Phenotype Data" to begin analysis.</p>
        <%= image_tag "start.svg", alt: "Step 5 - Process Phenotype Data" %>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>6. Wait a few seconds for the Ontology API to return results.</p>
        <%= image_tag "result.svg", alt: "Step 6 - Wait for Results" %>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>7. Results will be displayed below the input form.</p>
        <%= image_tag "result.svg", alt: "Step 7 - View Result" %>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</main>
